                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Reports / Studies</Header>
                <Paragraph>The FJC posts studies that were published in the past on its website in Portable Document Format (PDF) for downloading. Its Research Division conducted them. Some Center reports are not published or made publicly available due to restrictions in place from the source of the research request.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
